int.com/Consumer/ICrn1m7VU6y6Zv7kezOgJL/Simmba-movie-review-Crash-and-Burn.html|archive-date=28 December 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> With worldwide earnings of {{INRConvert|4|b}}, ''Simmba'' emerged as Singh's second [[List of Bollywood films of 2018|top-earning Indian film of 2018]].<ref name="2018w">
{{cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/box-office-collections/worldwide/2018/|title=Bollywood Top Grossers Worldwide: 2018|website=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=1 March 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301141625/https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/box-office-collections/worldwide/2018/|archive-date=1 March 2019|url-status=live}}
