ticleshow/67234455.cms|title=Ranveer Singh to play Dara Shikoh while Vicky Kaushal will be seen as Aurangzeb in 'Takht'|work=The Times of India|date=24 December 2018|access-date=25 December 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225091547/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/ranveer-singh-to-play-dara-shikoh-while-vicky-kaushal-will-be-seen-as-aurangzeb-in-takht/articleshow/67234455.cms|archive-date=25 December 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> He has also committed to team with Yash Raj Films once again for the comedy ''[[Jayeshbhai Jordaar]]''.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/ranveer-singh-on-bagging-jayeshbhai-jordaar-it-s-the-most-solid-on-paper-material-i-ve-come-across-1535425-2019-05-27|title=Ranveer Singh on bagging Jayeshbhai Jordaar: It's the most solid on-paper material I've come across|work=India Today|access-date=27 May 2019|date=27 May 2019}}</ref>

