Singh began dating Deepika Padukone, his co-star in ''Goliyon Ki Raasleela Ram-Leela'', in August 2012.<ref>{{cite news|title=Ranveer Singh: I haven't met anyone like Deepika Padukone, ever!|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/ranveer-singh-i-havent-met-anyone-like-deepika-padukone-ever/articleshow/67242687.cms|work=The Times of India|date=25 December 2018|accessdate=25 December 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226115953/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/ranveer-singh-i-havent-met-anyone-like-deepika-padukone-ever/articleshow/67242687.cms|archive-date=26 December 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> In October 2018, the couple announced their impending marriage.<ref>{{cite news|title=Deepika Padukone and Ranveer Singh announce wedding date|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/deepika-padukone-ranveer-singh-wedding-card-date-5411450/|work=The Indian Express|date=21 October 2018|accessdate=21 October 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021190905/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/deepika-padukone-ranveer-singh-wedding-card-date-5411450/|archive-date=21 October 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> The following month, they married in traditional [[Konkani]] [[Hindu]] and Sikh [[Anand Karaj]] (Singh's paternal grandfather is Sikh)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mid-day.com/photos/lesser-known-facts-about-ranveer-singh-before-he-became-a-star/17117|title=Lesser known facts about Ranveer Singh, before he became a star|website=mid-day|access-date=14 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109162430/https://www.mid-day.com/photos/lesser-known-facts-about-ranveer-singh-before-he-became-a-star/17117|archive-date=9 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> ceremonies at [[Lake Como]], Italy.<ref>{{cite news|title=Deepika Padukone, Ranveer Singh are married now, wedding ceremony ends in Italy|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/deepika-padukone-ranveer-singh-are-married-now-wedding-ceremony-ends-in-italy/story-OrrIJnMvTwI1wSwl7JbWqM.html|work=Hindustan Times|date=14 November 2018|accessdate=14 November 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181114143025/https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/deepika-padukone-ranveer-singh-are-married-now-wedding-ceremony-ends-in-italy/story-OrrIJnMvTwI1wSwl7JbWqM.html|archive-date=14 November 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/ranveer-singh-deepika-padukone-wedding-sikh-body-upset-over-anand-karaj-performed-outside-gurdwara/story-gtw6h2BVs7F2tCD3VjK85K.html|title=Ranveer Singh-Deepika Padukone wedding: Sikh body upset over Anand Karaj performed outside gurdwara|date=19 November 2018|accessdate=19 December 2018|work=Hindustan Times|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181219134548/https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/ranveer-singh-deepika-padukone-wedding-sikh-body-upset-over-anand-karaj-performed-outside-gurdwara/story-gtw6h2BVs7F2tCD3VjK85K.html|archive-date=19 December 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>

