-young-indians-of-2017-3790559.html|archive-date=22 August 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Sethi|first=Shikha|url=https://www.gqindia.com/influence-list/content/the-gq-50-most-influential-young-indians-of-2019|title=Here's the full list of GQ's 50 most influential young Indians of 2019|work=GQ|date=12 December 2019|accessdate=16 January 2020}}</ref> In 2019, ''[[India Today]]'' featured him among the nation's 50 most powerful people.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/the-most-powerful-people-of-india-2019-full-list-1574021-2019-07-26 |title=The most powerful people of India 2019 |work=India Today |date=26 July 2019 |accessdate=30 July 2019 }}</ref>

